Package: toxcms
Type: Package
Title: A tool to perform Metabolomic dose-response analysis and discover drug targets
Version: 1.0.3
Authors@R: c(
    person("Cong-Hui", "Yao", email = "conghui.yao@wustl.edu", role = c("aut")),
    person("Lingjue (Mike)", "Wang", email = "wang.lingjue@wustl.edu", role = c("cre","aut")),
    person("Ethan", "Stancliff", email = "estancliff@wustl.edu", role = c("ctb"))
    )
Description: An informatic tool for metabolomics data analysis. TOXcms profiles metabolic trends as a function
    of drug doses from untargeted metabolomics data, models and visualizes dose-dependent metabolic changes. 
    TOXcms is useful in screening metabolic targets of drugs.
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    utils,
    magrittr,
    data.table,
    dr4pl,
    dplyr,
    userfriendlyscience,
    stats,
    gplots,
    ggplot2,
    grDevices,
    gridExtra,
    ggfortify,
    hashmap
Suggests:
